2 We are lost amid the rapture of redeeming love:  Glory to God, hallelujah! 
 We are seeking every moment all its grace to prove:  Glory to God, hallelujah! 
3 We are going on to glory as the Lord has told: 
 Glory to God, hallelujah! 
